## Description {#details}

Class responsible for emitting a DWARF v5 Accelerator Table.

The only public function is <a href="#adf16303e57e2bd8a12ca84436de012be">emit()</a>, which performs the actual emission.

A callback abstracts the logic to provide a <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/cu">CU</a> index for a given entry.
